OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FPolice heard that a boy who was later
OL,7,Ffound in a storm drain had been
OL,8,Fbehaving "strangely" before he left
OL,9,Fhome for the final time, an inquest
OL,10,Fhas been told.
OL,12,FThe naked body of Noah Donohoe, 14,
OL,13,Fwas discovered in a storm drain tunnel
OL,14,Fin north Belfast in June 2020, six
OL,15,Fdays after he left home on his bike to
OL,16,Fmeet two friends in the Cavehill area
OL,17,Fof the city.
OL,26,@pD@JOUpD@TO]
