OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Gardiner was being
OL,7,Fquestioned at the inquest at Belfast
OL,8,Fcoroner's court about CCTV footage
OL,9,Fcollected from the Fitzroy Avenue area
OL,10,Fwhere Noah lived and about why the boy
OL,11,Fturned right after leaving his home.
OL,13,FBrenda Campbell KC, counsel for Noah's
OL,14,Fmother Fiona Donohoe, said he could
OL,15,Fhave turned left from his home to
OL,16,Freach the Ormeau Road, where he
OL,17,Feventually went.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
