PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1771956278
OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FMr Gardiner, who co-ordinated the CCTV
OL,7,Fin the investigation, said "that was
OL,8,Fnever asked", adding: "In terms of
OL,9,FCCTV, no. The priorities were
OL,10,Felsewhere.
OL,12,F"The information we had was that he
OL,13,Fwas behaving strangely in the house."
OL,15,FThe court heard "his mum had reported
OL,16,Fhim emotional".
OL,18,FMr Gardiner responded: "He lied about
OL,19,Fwhere he was going.
