OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Campbell said her line of
OL,7,Fquestioning about the CCTV footage is
OL,8,Fbecause she is "exploring the
OL,9,Flimitations of what we can understand
OL,10,Fabout Noah's journey based on the
OL,11,Flimitations of the evidence".
OL,13,FShe pointed out Noah being at the same
OL,14,Fplace at two different times, or in
OL,15,Fvarious places at the same time "which
OL,16,Fis not physically possible", according
OL,17,Fto the material gathered about the
OL,18,Froute he took.
