OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FThe court heard there was some footage
OL,7,Fcollected in 2020 that was not watched
OL,8,Funtil 2022.
OL,10,FAsked about why there was not more
OL,11,Fclips from the Holylands area, Mr
OL,12,FGardiner said that inquiries were
OL,13,Ftaking place over different Belfast
OL,14,Fareas.
OL,16,FHe said: "The priorities at this stage
OL,17,Fwere the route, the backpack and the
OL,18,Fphone."
OL,26,@xD@JOUzD@GO]
