OL,3,CPolice heard Noah Donohoe had been
OL,4,Cacting 'strangely', inquest hears
OL,6,FMs Campbell suggested "we never had a
OL,7,Ffull picture of his movements in the
OL,8,FHolylands when he left home for the
OL,9,Flast time", to which Mr Gardiner said
OL,10,F"no, we never".
